trans-unit.source: Cancel the dispatch of the selected order operations.

seg-source.mrk: Cancel the dispatch of the selected order operations.

target.mrk: 選択した指図作業の差立を取り消します。

trans-unit.source: By canceling the dispatch of an order operation, you take back the confirmation of work center and planned dates.

seg-source.mrk: By canceling the dispatch of an order operation, you take back the confirmation of work center and planned dates.

target.mrk: 指図作業の差立を取り消すと、作業区と計画日付の確認を取り消すことになります。

trans-unit.source: As a result, the app resets the processing status to <uicontrol>Due</uicontrol>. The <uicontrol>Must start on</uicontrol> constraint that is set automatically when an operation is dispatched, remains unchanged.

seg-source.mrk: As a result, the app resets the processing status to <uicontrol>Due</uicontrol>.
The <uicontrol>Must start on</uicontrol> constraint that is set automatically when an operation is dispatched, remains unchanged.

target.mrk: その結果、アプリでは処理ステータスが<uicontrol>期日</uicontrol>に再設定されます。
作業の差立時に自動的に設定される<uicontrol>必須開始日</uicontrol>制約は変更されません。

trans-unit.source: To enable this button, select at least one dispatched order operation. If you select multiple operations, and some of them have not yet been dispatched or are already in process, the processing status of these operations does not change.

seg-source.mrk: To enable this button, select at least one dispatched order operation.
If you select multiple operations, and some of them have not yet been dispatched or are already in process, the processing status of these operations does not change.

target.mrk: このボタンを有効化するには、少なくとも 1 つの差立済指図作業を選択します。
複数の作業を選択し、それらの一部が差立てられていないか、またはすでに処理中である場合、これらの作業の処理ステータスは変わりません。
